    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about" id="about">
      <h2>About Florida Blue (and why we're smiling)</h2>
      <p>
        Florida Blue is no ordinary health insurer. In fact, they’ve been
        bringing high‑quality, affordable care to the Sunshine State since
        1944, growing to serve nearly six million members along the way. They’re
        the largest single‑state provider of individual marketplace plans in the
        country and even opened customer centres in 2006 so members could speak
        face to face. With a mission like that, it’s no wonder their colour is
        blue—it goes with the ocean, the sky and the occasional punchline.
      </p>
      <div class="highlights">
        <div class="highlight">
          <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          <h3>Nearly 6 Million Members</h3>
          <p>
            That’s a lot of Floridians to keep smiling, but somehow Florida Blue
            makes it look as easy as lounging on the beach.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          <h3>Largest Marketplace Provider</h3>
          <p>
            Go big or go home?  Florida Blue chose both.  They’re the largest
            single‑state provider of individual marketplace plans in the U.S.
            because covering Floridians is their favorite pastime.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight">
          <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          <h3>Florida Blue Centers</h3>
